      "name": "CFD vs. experimental hemolysis index — FDA pump benchmark",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) against experimental measurements from the FDA pump benchmark study across 5 operating points. Mean relative error 8.3%; all predictions within ±15% of experimental values. Acceptance criterion met.",
